0.code:
S = 'ALAK'
K = 25
cnt = K
ans = ''
for s in S:
    if s == 'a':
        ans += 'a'
    elif cnt >= 123 - ord(s):
        cnt -= 123 - ord(s)
        ans += 'a'
    else:
        ans += s
last = ans[-1]
last = chr((ord(last) - 97 + cnt) % 26 + 97)
print(ans[:-1] + last)

alpha=list('abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz')
ans=[]
for i in range(len(s)):
    ki= 26-alpha.index(s[i]) if s[i]!='a' else 0
    if(i==len(s)-1):
        kn=k+alpha.index(s[i])
        kn=kn%26
        ans.append(alpha[kn])
    elif(ki<=k):
        ans.append('a')
        k-=ki
    else:
        ans.append(s[i])
print(''.join(ans))

alpha=list('abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz')
ans=[]
for i in range(len(s)):
    ki= 26-alpha.index(s[i]) if s[i]!='a' else 0
    if(i==len(s)-1):
        kn=k+alpha.index(s[i])
        kn=kn%26
        ans.append(alpha[kn])
    elif(ki<=k):
        ans.append('a')
        k-=ki
    else:
        ans.append(s[i])
print(''.join(ans))

        kn=kn%26
        ans.append(alpha[kn])
    elif(ki<=k):
        ans.append('a')
        k-=ki
    else:
        ans.append(s[i])
print(''.join(ans))
